{
  "stem": "13471.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, I asked him if he could take it up, and he said, yeah, he could do it for us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I asked him what he would charge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I wouldn't charge anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, charge nothing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What do you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, he says, this paper I'm running, he says, is on Hitler's press.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, Hitler owned this Nazi thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he says, we have his 10-million-mark bank account.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, what the hell better use could we put this to than to print the Nuremberg record?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we went back to Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the judges-- Lord Justice Lawrence was quite definite.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No, he says, we're not going to take tainted money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He said, I don't want anybody to be able to say, at any time in the future, that this is a put-up job.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This has got to be absolutely above approach-- reproach [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we got-- sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then Sieg-- all of a sudden Sieg comes to me, and he says, everything's working except the bindery.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I said, what's the matter with the bindery?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, he says, the Germans have laws about how much you can pay people for various different jobs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is a hangover from the Nazi days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the bindery needs so-and-so-- I think 35 girls-- to work for 30 marks a week to do this simple-- these simple jobs in the bindery.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I said, well, what's the matter with that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, he says, every one of those girls can find a GI boyfriend who will give them a pack of cigarettes that's worth 100 marks in a week, so why the hell should they work?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I says-- he says, we've got to get some PX goods to give them, in addition to these 30 marks.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
